{"tid":1655464,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先喺hkcc wk俾個男人問係咪示威者","createTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T12:37:27.000Z","uid":203234,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"93cebf376caadd80ead4e051be4e1dfeab1c03f7","tid":1655464,"uid":203234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今日戴帽戴口罩番學<br />\n落堂諗住搭shuttle兜左岀cc外圍嗰條街再行入停車場<br />\n有個男人見我咁嘅look走近問我係咪示威者<br />\n小弟通左兩晚頂好攰廢事搞咁多嘢<br />\n聲都唔岀淨係擰頭hea下佢好打發佢走咩都好啦<br />\n佢追問話唔係示威者又搞咁多嘢又戴口罩又剩<br />\n之後我就上左shuttle了<br />\n上車之後開車岀去見到有個男人企喺個扶手電梯隔離<br />\n利申:攰得滯無點理佢連樣都無望清楚<br />\n希望無認錯人<br />\n各位師兄姐師弟妹同手腳小心<br />\n屌你老母依家唔舒服唔戴得口罩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wYvFwcm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwYvFwcm.jpg&h=9b1cf196&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"106b4d4e2a5321e6894d2bda0f919d387ca4f8f8","tid":1655464,"uid":203234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7bab55b89b905f28e1bf8cf8b2142b9ca344b9b","tid":1655464,"uid":203234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a27f117f970170f51c8584b426c910eddb9eaaf","tid":1655464,"uid":234402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"叫保安啦"},{"pid":"b58f10f65334bd94e9c29ab2a40dab365af66196","tid":1655464,"uid":301906,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"叫保安睇實呢條友 驚佢精神有問題會發癲打人"},{"pid":"44fa40ac52b42626c2562ab85b56900f3a9b212f","tid":1655464,"uid":203234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"小弟上咗shuttle走左<br />\n有無人見到佢仲喺度又可以得閒嗌一嗌保安"},{"pid":"8356e24881be3a31958c990d20f9b930236d99ef","tid":1655464,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig